'''湯瑪士·-{zh-tw:喬瑟夫;zh-cn:约瑟夫;zh-hk:祖瑟夫;}-·「湯姆」·麥卡錫'''（{{lang-en|Thomas Joseph "Tom" McCarthy}}，{{bd|1966年|6月7日||}}）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.filmreference.com/film/15/Thomas-McCarthy.html|title=Thomas McCarthy Biography ((?)-)|publisher=|accessdate=2015-12-11|archive-date=2015-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151213043322/http://www.filmreference.com/film/15/Thomas-McCarthy.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wwd.com/eye/people/boys-night-out-with-tom-mccarthy-3679151|title=Boys’ Night Out With Tom McCarthy|author=Jessica Iredale|work=WWD|accessdate=2015-12-11|archive-date=2015-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208164228/http://wwd.com/eye/people/boys-night-out-with-tom-mccarthy-3679151/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[美国电影|美国电影]]导演、编剧和演员，执导的主要电影有《[[下一站，幸福_(電影)|下一站，幸福]]》、《[[不速之客|不速之客]]》和《[[驚爆焦點|驚爆焦點]]》。他以自編自導的2015年電影《[[驚爆焦點|驚爆焦點]]》獲得[[第88屆奧斯卡金像獎|第88屆奧斯卡金像獎]][[奧斯卡最佳影片獎|最佳影片獎]]和[[奧斯卡最佳原創劇本獎|最佳原創電影劇本獎]]。

==生平==
麥卡錫生长于[[新泽西州|新泽西州]]的New Providence，是家里5个孩子中的一员<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/thomas-mccarthy-on-his-first-cast-1426695361|title=Thomas McCarthy on His First Cast|date=18 March 2015|work=WSJ|accessdate=2015-12-11|archive-date=2015-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151124201856/http://www.wsj.com/articles/thomas-mccarthy-on-his-first-cast-1426695361|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nj.com/independentpress/index.ssf/2013/03/obituary_eugene_f_mccarthy_of.html|title=Obituary: Eugene F. McCarthy of New Providence|work=NJ.com|accessdate=2015-12-11|archive-date=2015-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151220150248/http://www.nj.com/independentpress/index.ssf/2013/03/obituary_eugene_f_mccarthy_of.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，父亲Eugene F. "Gene" McCarthy在纺织厂工作<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2011/may/20/thomas-mccarthy-win-win|title=The 'man strength' behind Win Win's Thomas McCarthy|author=Hermione Hoby|work=the Guardian|accessdate=2015-12-11|archive-date=2016-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160120151720/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2011/may/20/thomas-mccarthy-win-win|dead-url=no}}</ref>。毕业于[[耶鲁大学|耶鲁大学]]戏剧学院。

麥卡錫执导的首部电影《[[下一站，幸福_(電影)|下一站，幸福]]》赢得2003年[[圣丹斯影展|圣丹斯影展]]观众奖和编剧奖，以及[[英国电影学院奖|英国电影学院奖]]最佳原创剧本和[[独立精神奖|独立精神奖]]最佳编剧处女作奖。第二部作品《[[不速之客|不速之客]]》在2007年[[多伦多影展|多伦多影展]]上首映，赢得独立精神奖最佳导演奖<ref>{{cite journal
